Interface ItsNatHTMLInputTextFormatted

    public interface ItsNatHTMLInputTextFormatted
extends ItsNatHTMLInputText, ItsNatFormattedTextField
    Is the interface of ItsNatFormattedTextField components using HTML input text elements as user interface.

    ItsNat provides a default implementation of this interface.
